    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-title fade-in">
        <p class="sec-en">LOCAL EXPERIENCE</p>
        <h2 class="sec-ja">周辺おすすめスポット</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="area-card fade-in">
          <span class="area-badge">カフェ</span>
          <h3>レタンプリュス</h3>
          <p>地元で人気のおしゃれなカフェ。こだわりのコーヒーとスイーツでひと休み。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="area-card fade-in">
          <span class="area-badge">インテリア</span>
          <h3>LIANTIQE</h3>
          <p>センスあふれるアンティーク家具のショップ。空間づくりのインスピレーションに。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="area-card fade-in">
          <span class="area-badge">スパ・温浴</span>
          <h3>スパメッツァおおたか</h3>
          <p>大型スパ施設でリフレッシュ。サウナ・岩盤浴など充実した施設が揃います。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== SNS / NOTE ========== -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary" id="sns">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-title fade-in">
        <p class="sec-en">JOURNAL</p>
        <h2 class="sec-ja">最新情報</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="sns-grid">
        <!-- note -->
        <div class="sns-col fade-in">
          <div class="sns-head">
            <p class="sns-platform">note — FLUX HOUSEマガジン</p>
          </div>
          {noteItems.length > 0 ? (
            <ul class="note-list">
              {noteItems.map((item) => (
                <li class="note-item">
                  <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <p class="note-title">{item.title}</p>
                    {item.description && <p class="note-desc">{item.description}…</p>}
                    <p class="note-date">{item.pubDate}</p>
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          ) : (
            <div class="sns-empty">
              <a href="https://note.com/jin_sariimama/m/mbada4e66a2a3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">noteを読む →</a>
            </div>
          )}
          <a href="https://note.com/jin_sariimama/m/mbada4e66a2a3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="sns-more">すべての記事を読む →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Instagram -->
        <div class="sns-col fade-in">
          <div class="sns-head">
            <p class="sns-platform">Instagram — @fluxhouse_nagareyama</p>
          </div>
          {BEHOLD_FEED_ID ? (
            <behold-widget feed-id={BEHOLD_FEED_ID}></behold-widget>
          ) : (
            <div class="ig-placeholder">
              <p>最新の写真はInstagramで発信中</p>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline">Instagramを見る</a>
            </div>
          )}
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="sns-more">Instagramをフォローする →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== MINPAKU ========== -->
  <section class="section bg-dark" id="minpaku">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="minpaku-inner fade-in">
        <span class="badge">Coming Soon</span>
        <div class="sec-title" style="margin-top:20px;">
          <p class="sec-en">STAY</p>
          <h2 class="sec-ja">民泊・住宅宿泊事業 準備中</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="minpaku-text">
          FLUX HOUSEでは、住宅宿泊事業（民泊）の開始に向けて準備を進めています。<br />
          「泊まる」ことでより深くこの場所と南流山を体験できるよう、<br />
          準備が整い次第Instagramにてお知らせします。
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline">
          Instagramをフォローする
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== CONTACT ========== -->
  <section class="section bg-primary" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-inner fade-in">
        <div class="sec-title">
          <p class="sec-en">CONTACT</p>
          <h2 class="sec-ja">お問い合わせ</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="contact-text">
          ご予約・空き状況の確認・その他のご質問は、<br />下記のフォームからお気軽にどうぞ。<br />
          通常2〜3営業日以内にご返信いたします。
        </p>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/MAnhrqk2x8Rn2JWD7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline">
          お問い合わせ・空き状況を確認する
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== FOOTER ========== -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-logo">
        <img src="/fluxhouse_logo_tate_white.png" alt="FLUX HOUSE" class="footer-logo-img" />
      </div>
      <nav class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://note.com/jin_sariimama/m/mbada4e66a2a3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">note</a>
        <a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">©2026 FLUX HOUSE</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ============================================================
     LAYOUT BACKGROUNDS
     ============================================================ */
  .bg-primary   { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .bg-secondary { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .bg-dark      { background: var(--bg-dark); }

  /* ============================================================
     SECTION BASE
     ============================================================ */
  .section {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: 130px 0;
    }
  }

  /* ============================================================
     SECTION TITLE  (英語大文字 + 日本語)
     ============================================================ */
  .sec-title {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .sec-en {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8c8c8c;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .sec-en--light {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .sec-ja {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .sec-ja--light {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  /* ============================================================
     HEADER
     ============================================================ */
  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .header-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 80px;
    padding-top: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header-inner {
      height: 96px;
    }
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo-img {
    height: 36px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .logo-img {
      height: 48px;
    }
  }

  .nav-desktop {
    display: none;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .nav-desktop a {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    position: relative;
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .nav-desktop a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    transition: width var(--transition);
  }

  .nav-desktop a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .nav-desktop a:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nav-desktop { display: flex; }
    .hamburger   { display: none; }
  }

  .hamburger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 5px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 8px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .hamburger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-text);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(6.5px) rotate(45deg); }
  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-6.5px) rotate(-45deg); }

  .mobile-menu {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
    background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.98);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .mobile-menu.open { max-height: 320px; }

  .mobile-menu nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 16px 24px 24px;
  }

  .mobile-nav-link {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .mobile-nav-link:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .mobile-nav-link:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  /* ============================================================
     HERO
     ============================================================ */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, #4A3020 0%, #2C2017 60%, #1A1209 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 24px 80px;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 15% 70%, rgba(139,111,71,0.4) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 85% 20%, rgba(184,150,106,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .hero-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .btn-hero {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
